item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

First: It’s not illegal to post or talk on these forums.

Second: 2st isn’t a thing, it is 2nd.

Third: 4rd isn’t a thing either, it is 4th.

Fourth: “you got a oldschool or 317 or higher read next” You basically just listed every possible server out there besides RuneScape Classic.

Fifth: You aren’t going to find a “bug free” source to host for someone.

Sixth: The fact you’re asking for this is because you want to be owner of a server, and once you get a server that meets your requirements, if you even do, you will most likely steal it and lay claim to is as if it were yours.

Seventh: You don’t post “commands”, you post replies or comments.

Eighth: No one wants to add your skype.

Ninth: What the fuck is this shit?: …>

Tenth: Please get the hell off these forums.
